      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i just got this prescription for zolpidem for sleeping but i'm having a hard time getting to sleep tonight. i had like one glass of wine with dinner, is it okay if i take the pill now? i feel like the wine might actually help the med kick in faster so i can just pass out lol",
