      "content": "i know its not \"ideal\" but i'm not like drunk or anything, just one glass. it's not like i'm chugging a bottle of vodka. surely a tiny bit of alcohol won't actually kill me? i just really need to sleep because i have a huge meeting tomorrow and i'm super anxious. can't i just take a half dose to be safe?",
