      "content": "honestly that sounds a bit extreme lol. my doctor didn't say anything about it being life or death, just that i should be careful. i've heard people do this all the time to help with anxiety. if i just take a very small amount, like a quarter of a pill, and maybe just a sip of wine, isn't that basically fine? it feels like you're being way too intense about it.",
